---
id: output-validator
name: "Output Validator"
version: 0.0.1
description: "Validate LLM output against an expected format specification. Checks schema compliance, required fields, types, and constraints."
system: ../systems/output-validator.md
parameters:
  - name: output
    type: string
    required: true
    description: "The LLM-generated output to validate"
  - name: expected_format
    type: string
    required: true
    description: "The expected format specification. Can be a JSON schema, a plain-text description of expected structure, or an example of valid output."
  - name: format_type
    type: string
    required: false
    enum: ["json_schema", "example", "description"]
    default: "json_schema"
    description: "How to interpret the expected_format parameter"
  - name: strict_mode
    type: boolean
    required: false
    default: false
    description: "When true, extra fields not in the schema are treated as errors instead of warnings"
  - name: required_fields
    type: json
    required: false
    description: "Explicit list of field paths that must be present (e.g., ['$.name', '$.results[*].score'])"
    default: []
---

# Output Validation Task

Validate the following LLM output against the expected format.

**Format type:** {{ format_type }}
**Strict mode:** {{ strict_mode }}

## Expected Format

{{ expected_format }}

{% if required_fields | length > 0 %}

## Required Fields

These fields must be present and non-empty:

{% for field in required_fields %}
- `{{ field }}`
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}

## Output to Validate

{{ output }}

## Required Output Format

```json
{
  "valid": <boolean>,
  "parseable": <boolean, could the output be parsed at all>,
  "error_count": <number>,
  "warning_count": <number>,
  "violations": [
    {
      "path": "<JSON path e.g. $.results[0].score>",
      "type": "<missing_field|wrong_type|invalid_value|extra_field|format_error|parse_error>",
      "severity": "<error|warning>",
      "expected": "<what was expected>",
      "actual": "<what was found>",
      "message": "<human readable description>"
    }
  ],
  "summary": "<one sentence summary>"
}
```